'''PROM'''
# [[Program]]mable [[Read]]-[[Only]] [[Memory]].  A PROM chip can be programmed one or more times (depending on the type) and generally cannot be re-programmed without special equipment.  Once programmed and installed in a device, it functions as a read-only chip (as if it had been [[hard-wired]] to function that way.)